msgid "Alright, let's see..."
msgstr "好吧，讓我看看..."

msgid "According to my notes..."
msgstr "依據我的筆記..."

msgid "I need to move the desks to the sides in all three classrooms."
msgstr "我需要把一共三間教室的桌子移到旁邊。"

msgid "Then I can draw a \"path\" in the middle of each one with chalk."
msgstr "接著我可以用粉筆在每間教室中間畫出一條\"路徑\"。"

msgid "Well, I'll leave the chalk drawing for last. I want to gather everything I need first."
msgstr "好吧，我會把用粉筆畫線留到最後。我想要先收集所有必要的東西。"

msgid "Oh no..."
msgstr "喔不..."

msgid "What are you doing...? Is this part of the ritual?"
msgstr "妳在做什麼...？這也是儀式的一部分嗎？"

msgid "Um... what's wrong with you?"
msgstr "呃...妳有什麼毛病？"

msgid "If this ritual involves the mass genocide of harmless plants, then I want nothing to do with it."
msgstr "如果這個儀式包含了無害植物大屠殺，那我不想和它有任何關係。"

msgid "Agreed."
msgstr "同意。"

msgid "Are you seriously going to go around killing all the plants?"
msgstr "妳真的打算到處殺死這些植物？"

msgid "I knew you were a psychopath..."
msgstr "我就知道妳是個瘋子..."

msgid "Sorry Kat, but we didn't sign up for this."
msgstr "抱歉凱特，我們打算不參加了。"

msgid "I don't like this ritual anymore..."
msgstr "我開始不喜歡這個儀式了..."

msgid "Don't worry Kaya, we're going home now."
msgstr "別擔心香耶，我們要回家了。"

msgid "Don't talk to us again."
msgstr "別再跟我們說話了。"

msgid "Shelves for the students to place their school bags."
msgstr "讓學生放書包的架子。"

msgid "There are no bags right now though."
msgstr "不過現在沒有書包。"

msgid "Everything's ready."
msgstr "都準備好了。"

msgid "All that's left is to wait 5 minutes and then burn the hair."
msgstr "現在只要等 5 分鐘再把頭髮燒掉。"

msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "This is going to be such a pain to clean up."
msgstr "這一定會很難清理。"

msgid "Seriously? Stop messing with things!"
msgstr "別再惹是生非了！"

msgid "But everything I \"mess with\" ends up being a scam."
msgstr "可是我\"惹上\"的東西最後都只是騙人的。"

msgid "What if some day it isn't?"
msgstr "如果哪天不是騙人的呢？"

msgid "What if you end up summoning some ghost or the devil and condemning your soul to an eternity in the netherworld?"
msgstr "如果妳召喚了什麼妖魔鬼怪然後把妳送到十八層地獄呢？"

msgid "What if your soul is already damned!?"
msgstr "如果妳早就被詛咒了呢！？"

msgid "Then I guess that's what's waiting for me after I die."
msgstr "那我大概會在死後受到報應吧。"

msgid "KAT!"
msgstr "凱特！"

msgid "It was a joke!"
msgstr "我只是在開玩笑！"

msgid "You're not gonna find him this way, you know?"
msgstr "妳這樣是找不到他的，妳知道吧？"

msgid "You'll just do whatever you want no matter what I say, won't you?"
msgstr "不管我說什麼妳都不會改變吧？"

msgid "It's possible."
msgstr "有可能。"

msgid "Stubborn idiot."
msgstr "固執的笨蛋。"

msgid "I prefer \"ambitious idiot\"."
msgstr "請叫我\"有理想的笨蛋\"。"

msgid "So... will you tell me where the letter is?"
msgstr "那...妳可以告訴我那封信在哪嗎？"

msgid "You exhaust me Kat, you know that?"
msgstr "妳讓我很累，妳知道嗎？"

msgid "And yet here we are."
msgstr "然而我們現在還在說話。"

msgid "Fine. You win. It's in the occult club."
msgstr "好吧。妳贏了。信在超自然研究社。"

msgid "There's a golden envelope in one of the drawers. But they won't let you sniff around since you're not a member."
msgstr "其中一個抽屜裡有金色信封。不過他們不會讓你到處亂翻，因為妳不是社員。"

msgid "Thanks, you're the best!"
msgstr "謝啦，妳最棒了！"

msgid "Huh?"
msgstr "嗯？"

msgid "(Is there somebody at the door..?)"
msgstr "(門後有人嗎？)"

msgid "Alright, now I just have to blow the candles off. So let's-"
msgstr "好，現在我只要把蠟燭吹熄。來-"

msgid "Huh? The candles... Did they just...?"
msgstr "嗯？蠟燭...自己就...？"

msgid "...I guess I should count to 100..."
msgstr "...我想我應該數到 100..."

msgid "1, 2, 3, 4, 5..."
msgstr "1、2、3、4、5..."

msgid "...28, 29, 30..."
msgstr "...28、29、30..."

msgid "(Why am I doing this? This ridiculous game couldn't possibly work.)"
msgstr "(我在做什麼？這可笑的遊戲怎麼可能會有用。)"

msgid "...55, 56, 57, 58..."
msgstr "...55、56、57、58..."

msgid "(I wonder if mom is worried about me...)"
msgstr "(媽媽會不會很擔心我...)"

msgid "(Huh? What was that?)"
msgstr "(嗯？那是什麼？)"

msgid "...79, 80, 81..."
msgstr "...79、80、81..."

msgid "(What's all that noise!?)"
msgstr "(這吵鬧聲是怎麼回事？)"

msgid "Is anyone there...?"
msgstr "有人嗎？"

msgid "...97, 98, 99..."
msgstr "...97、98、99..."

msgid "...100."
msgstr "...100。"

msgid "So... I... open my eyes?"
msgstr "那麼...我...該張開眼睛？"

msgid "It... worked?"
msgstr "成功...了？"

msgid "It worked?"
msgstr "成功了？"

msgid "It worked!! I can't believe it!"
msgstr "成功了！！！不可置信！"

msgid "This is incredible!!"
msgstr "太神奇了！！"

msgid "But... where am I?"
msgstr "不過...我在哪裡？"

msgid "It's a... hallway? It definitely isn't the school."
msgstr "這裡是...走廊？絕對不是在學校。"

msgid "This is unbelievable, how could it have worked?"
msgstr "太不可思議了，為什麼這會有用？"

msgid "It doesn't make any logical sense. I was in the classroom a minute ago. Have I gone mad?"
msgstr "這沒道理啊。我剛剛還在教室裡。我是發瘋了嗎？"

msgid "THIS IS SO EXCITING, I CAN'T BELIEVE IT WORKED!"
msgstr "太讓我興奮了，沒想到會有用！"

msgid "If I wake up from this and it turns out to be a dream... well... that would be disappointing, to say the least."
msgstr "如果我醒來發現這只是一場夢...那麼...我會很失望，至少可以這麼說。"

msgid "Okay. I definitely need to check this place out."
msgstr "好。我得瞧瞧這個地方。"

msgid "Do you wish to save your progress?"
msgstr "是否要儲存你的進度？"

msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "Now what?"
msgstr "現在呢？"

msgid "Now we just wait 5 minutes."
msgstr "現在我們要等 5 分鐘。"

msgid "Doing nothing?"
msgstr "什麼也不做？"

msgid "Peace and quiet are not as bad as you imagine."
msgstr "平靜不如你想像的糟。"

msgid "After that, I'll burn the hair and you help me blow out the candles one by one."
msgstr "在那之後，我會把頭髮燒掉，然後妳們幫我把蠟燭一根一根吹熄。"

msgid "Burnt hair smells bad..."
msgstr "燒焦的頭髮很臭..."

msgid "It does."
msgstr "是啊。"

msgid "But it's the last step, might as well do it right."
msgstr "不過這是最後一步，最好好好做完。"

msgid "What happens then?"
msgstr "然後會發生什麼事？"

msgid "No idea."
msgstr "不知道。"

msgid "Really?"
msgstr "真的嗎？"

msgid "We probably just clean up and go home. These rituals are a scam, you know?"
msgstr "大概就把這裡清理乾淨再回家。妳們不知道這種儀式都是騙人的？"

msgid "So... you're just making us make a mess, so that we can help you clean it up?"
msgstr "所以...妳只是讓我們把這裡搞得一團亂，再讓我們幫妳清理乾淨？"

msgid "What's the matter, are you not entertained?"
msgstr "怎麼了，妳覺得不好玩嗎？"

msgid "...Tsk."
msgstr "...咋。"

msgid "I think it's time."
msgstr "時間應該到了。"

msgid "Finally!"
msgstr "終於！"

msgid "Now I just burn this..."
msgstr "我只要燒掉這..."

msgid "Quickly, put out the candles now!"
msgstr "快，把蠟燭熄掉！"

msgid "Now, shut your eyes and be quiet while I count to one hundred, okay?"
msgstr "現在，把眼睛閉上並保持安靜讓我數到一百，可以嗎？"

msgid "Got it."
msgstr "知道了。"

msgid "Alright then, I'll start."
msgstr "好，我要數了。"

msgid "Shhh!"
msgstr "噓噓噓！"

msgid "(Huh...?)"
msgstr "(嗯？)"

msgid "(What the hell was that!?)"
msgstr "(那是什麼鬼！？)"

msgid "...94, 95, 96, 97, 98, 99, 100!"
msgstr "...94、95、96、97、98、99、100！"

msgid "Huh...?"
msgstr "嗯？"

msgid "What the...?"
msgstr "怎麼回事...？"

msgid "Are those...?"
msgstr "那些是...？"

msgid "Well... my lines aren't perfect, but it should do the job!"
msgstr "好吧...畫得不夠完美，但這應該就夠了！"

msgid "I need to do this in all three rooms."
msgstr "我需要在一共三間教室都做一次。"

msgid "Two down, one to go."
msgstr "兩間好了，剩下一間。"

msgid "That night... I got cold feet, I guess."
msgstr "那天晚上...我卻步了...應該吧。"

msgid "I went home without completing the ritual."
msgstr "我沒有完成儀式就回家了。"

msgid "Despite that, I made plans to try again."
msgstr "儘管如此，我打算再試一次。"

msgid "However, both my notes and the letter had disappeared without a trace."
msgstr "可是，我的筆記和信件都不翼而飛。"

msgid "I tried telling myself that maybe the ritual was a scam anyways..."
msgstr "我試著說服自己反正儀式是騙人的..."

msgid "But now... how will I ever know?"
msgstr "可是...我要怎麼確認呢？"

msgid "Dead End K2 - Cold Kat Feet"
msgstr "死路 K2 - 冰冷的貓腳 (Cold Kat Feet)"

msgid "What's... going on?"
msgstr "現在是...怎麼回是？"

msgid "These stairs are making no sense right now."
msgstr "這樓梯一點道理也沒有。"

msgid "This building has only 3 floors. I've taken these stairs every day..."
msgstr "這棟建築只有 3 層樓。我每天都爬著這些樓梯..."

msgid "I must be really tired. I'll just go down without thinking."
msgstr "我一定是累了。接著就什麼都不想下樓吧。"

msgid "I can't... get anywhere..."
msgstr "我沒辦法...到任何地方..."

msgid "Am I dreaming right now?"
msgstr "我在做夢嗎？"

msgid "I think I'll just... rest here."
msgstr "我想我就...在這裡休息吧。"

msgid "Tomorrow morning... someone will wake me up."
msgstr "明天早上...會有人來叫醒我。"

msgid "Hopefully at home, in my own bed."
msgstr "最好是在家裡，我自己的床上。"

msgid "The next time I woke up, I was still in the same place."
msgstr "下一次醒來時，我還在同一個地方。"

msgid "I tried again. Going up, going down... it made no difference."
msgstr "我試了又是。往上、往下...沒有任何差別。"

msgid "I decided to make an experiment with chalk."
msgstr "我決定用粉筆來做個實驗。"

msgid "Logic would dictate that this X isn't here if I go up or down a floor."
msgstr "邏輯上來說這個 X 記號不會在我上下樓後出現。"

msgid "I'm... trapped..."
msgstr "我被...困住了..."

msgid "I don't think I'm going to make it home tonight either..."
msgstr "我想我今晚也不會回家了..."

msgid "Sorry Mom."
msgstr "對不起媽媽。"

msgid "Dead End K3 - Academic Spiral"
msgstr "死路 K3 - 學術螺旋"

msgid "And so, we went home without completing the ritual."
msgstr "最後，我們沒有完成儀式就回家了。"

msgid "For some reason, I lost interest after that."
msgstr "不知為何，我在那之後就失去了興趣。"

msgid "In exchange, I gained some new people to talk to."
msgstr "取而代之，我認識了一些可以交談的人。"

msgid "Well, I suppose the ritual couldn't have been that important anyways."
msgstr "好吧，我猜那個儀式大概也沒那麼重要。"

msgid "Dead End K4 - Nevermind Forever"
msgstr "死路 K4 - 還是別再想了吧"

msgid "You know, despite the rules,"
msgstr "妳知道嗎，雖然規則寫在那裡，"

msgid "every so often some moron thinks they can bring in an entire group."
msgstr "偶爾還是會有蠢蛋覺得他們可以整組進來。"

msgid "Huh? Who's there?"
msgstr "嗯？誰在那裡？"

msgid "Where is this place...?"
msgstr "這裡是哪裡...？"

msgid "I would have at least made it interesting for you."
msgstr "我原本還打算讓妳感到有趣。"

msgid "But now? Forget it."
msgstr "現在呢？算了吧。"

msgid "What? Wait-!"
msgstr "什麼？等等-！"

msgid "Dead End K5 - Party Wipe"
msgstr "死路 K5 - 團滅"

msgid "Once they were gone, I felt a bit guilty so I went home as well."
msgstr "她們走了之後，我感到有點過意不去所以也回家了。"

msgid "Maybe I'll try the ritual again, some other time."
msgstr "也許我可以之後再試試這個儀式。"

msgid "Next time, I hope not to run into anyone."
msgstr "下一次，希望不會遇到其他人。"

msgid "Dead End K6 - Snip snip"
msgstr "死路 K6 - 喀擦喀擦"

msgid "And so, we left the school and walked home."
msgstr "最後，我們離開學校並走路回家。"

msgid "No one said anything for a while."
msgstr "一段時間都沒有人說話。"

msgid "(I think Kat is feeling down...)"
msgstr "(我覺得凱特心情不好...)"

msgid "(Yeah.)"
msgstr "(是啊。)"

msgid "(Should we do something?)"
msgstr "(我們該做些什麼嗎？)"

msgid "(What's on your mind?)"
msgstr "(妳有什麼想法？)"

msgid "(I don't know...)"
msgstr "(我不知道...)"

msgid "(Do you think Kat likes to sing?)"
msgstr "(妳覺得凱特喜歡唱歌嗎？)"

msgid "(Hmmm...)"
msgstr "(哼~~...)"

msgid "(Good idea, Saki!)"
msgstr "(好主意，沙紀！)"

msgid "(Haven't seen you this excited about karaoke before, Kaya...)"
msgstr "(沒看過妳對唱卡拉OK這麼興奮，香耶...)"

msgid "(That's a yes, then?)"
msgstr "(那就說定囉？)"

msgid "(Alright.)"
msgstr "(好吧。)"

msgid "So..."
msgstr "那麼..."

msgid "We were thinking of going to this place..."
msgstr "我們想說要去個地方..."

msgid "(I can't do this! She's ignoring me!)"
msgstr "(沒有用！她無視我！)"

msgid "Kat!"
msgstr "凱特！"

msgid "Hmm?"
msgstr "嗯？"

msgid "Come with us."
msgstr "跟我們走。"

msgid "Just come."
msgstr "來就對了。"

msgid "Sure, whatever."
msgstr "好吧，隨便。"

msgid "(You're so good!)"
msgstr "(妳好強！)"

msgid "(Are they trying... to cheer me up...?)"
msgstr "(她們是在試著...讓我高興嗎...？)"

msgid "(Maybe... things are better this way.)"
msgstr "(也許...這樣比較好。)"

msgid "(I need to believe that much, at least.)"
msgstr "(我需要相信著，至少如此。)"

msgid "Dead End K7 - Girls' Night Out"
msgstr "死路 K7 - 女孩的夜晚"

msgid "I didn't hear from the voice again."
msgstr "我沒有再聽到聲音了。"

msgid "But, no matter how much I wanted to, I didn't scream for help."
msgstr "但是，無論我多麼想要，我仍然沒有大喊救命。"

msgid "Someone will come for me... eventually."
msgstr "有人會來找到我...一定會的。"

msgid "I just know it."
msgstr "我深信不疑。"

msgid "Dead End K8 - My Way"
msgstr "死路 K8 - 我的道路"

msgid "We're... back here?"
msgstr "我們...回到這裡了？"

msgid "Maybe this is the school's way of saying \"You can't leave now.\""
msgstr "也許這是學校對我們說\"妳們現在不能離開\"的方法。"

msgid "How can you just say something like that?"
msgstr "妳怎麼可以這麼說？"

msgid "Are we going home soon...?"
msgstr "我們要回家了嗎...？"

msgid "I think I'll pass on burning the school down today."
msgstr "我想我不打算今天把學校燒掉。"

msgid "Wow, thank you for your generosity."
msgstr "哇，感謝妳的大恩大德。"

msgid "What are you doing? I thought you were busy."
msgstr "妳在做什麼？我以為妳很忙。"

msgid "I'm just taking a break."
msgstr "只是休息一下。"

msgid "Is that so..."
msgstr "是喔..."

msgid "Are you scared? You're scared, aren't you?"
msgstr "妳怕了嗎？妳怕了，對吧？"

msgid "Did you come to us for comfort?"
msgstr "妳來找我們取暖嗎？"

msgid "The only scary thing here is that attitude of yours."
msgstr "這裡唯一可怕的是妳的態度。"

msgid "She's still upset at you messing up our night, as you can see."
msgstr "她還在因為妳搗亂了我們的活動生氣，妳也看得出來。"

msgid "It's okay to be scared..."
msgstr "會害怕是很正常的..."

msgid "Oh, I know! Why don't you show us your ritual as an apology?"
msgstr "喔，我想到了！妳可以讓我們看看妳的儀式來當表達歉意？"

msgid "I'm kind of interested, too."
msgstr "我也有點興趣。"

msgid "Well, the rules say..."
msgstr "可是，規則提到..."

msgid "Oh come on, you don't ACTUALLY think it's gonna work, do you? It's just a game, as you said."
msgstr "拜託，妳不會以為這是真的吧？這只是個遊戲，就像妳說的。"

msgid "The rules don't actually matter."
msgstr "規則沒那麼重要。"

msgid "I suppose not."
msgstr "我想也是。"

msgid "Then it's decided, we will tag along with you."
msgstr "那就這麼決定了，我們會跟著妳。"

msgid "You're tasked with entertaining us now."
msgstr "妳現在的工作是娛樂我們。"

msgid "Well, I suppose it can't be helped."
msgstr "好吧，我想也沒其他辦法了。"

msgid "Let's go, then."
msgstr "那麼我們走吧。"

msgid "I'm back in this hallway..."
msgstr "我又回到了這條走廊..."

msgid "I don't like this... I need to get out of here..."
msgstr "我不喜歡這裡...我必須離開這裡..."

msgid "Whoa... weird dream."
msgstr "哇...好奇怪的夢。"

msgid "Everyone must be gone already."
msgstr "大家一定都走了。"

msgid "Looks like it's eleven... I should get to it."
msgstr "十一點了...我該開始行動了。"

msgid "Ohhhh no..."
msgstr "喔喔喔不不不..."

msgid "You moved it!!"
msgstr "妳動了它！！"

msgid "I didn't, I swear! You know I hate this type of thing!"
msgstr "沒有，我發誓！妳知道我討厭這種東西！"

msgid "This can't possibly be happening..."
msgstr "這怎麼可能發生..."

msgid "It spelled \"DIE\"!!-"
msgstr "它拼出了\"去死\"！！-"

msgid "Oh my... Oh no..."
msgstr "喔...喔不..."

msgid "Stop joking around!! This is serious!!"
msgstr "別開玩笑了！！我是認真的！"

msgid "...Aah.... we should not have played this..."
msgstr "...啊...我們不該玩這的..."

msgid "I TOLD you we're going to be cursed!!"
msgstr "我跟妳說過我們會被詛咒！！"

msgid "WHAT WAS THAT!?"
msgstr "那是什麼！？"

msgid "Is that a ghost?? We summoned a ghost!"
msgstr "是鬼魂嗎？我們召喚了鬼魂！"

msgid "oh my god oh my god oh my god oh my god-"
msgstr "天哪天哪天哪天哪-"

msgid "YOU'RE MAKING TOO MUCH NOISE"
msgstr "妳們也太大聲了"

msgid "Oh...It's just Kat..."
msgstr "喔...是凱特..."

msgid "What's with the crazy knocking? What was that for!?"
msgstr "妳幹嘛要狂敲門！？"

msgid "Did that spook you? You're not supposed to be here, you know?"
msgstr "嚇到妳了嗎？妳們不該出現在這裡，知道嗎？"

msgid "I could say the same about you. Why are YOU here?"
msgstr "妳還不是一樣。為什麼妳在這裡？"

msgid "Actually..."
msgstr "事實上..."

msgid "Say hello to the new member of the occult club!"
msgstr "跟超自然研究社的新社員打招呼！"

msgid "I had the wonderful opportunity to meet all of the members yesterday."
msgstr "我昨天有幸和所有社員見面。"

msgid "I don't recall seeing you there."
msgstr "我不記得在那裡看到妳們。"

msgid "You three are not part of the club, are you?"
msgstr "妳們三個不是社員吧？"

msgid "That's funny. I didn't pin you of all people as the \"occult\" type, Kat."
msgstr "真有趣。我沒想到妳是喜歡\"超自然\"的人，凱特。"

msgid "That's because I'm not."
msgstr "那是因為我不是。"

msgid "H-Hey!! We were doing something here!"
msgstr "嘿-嘿！！我們在做事！"

msgid "I'll save you the trouble. All three of you moved it."
msgstr "我來幫妳們省去麻煩。妳們三個都動了它。"

msgid "Wha...?"
msgstr "什...？"

msgid "The planchette. From your game. You all moved it. There's no ghost in the room."
msgstr "那個妳們用來玩遊戲的板子。妳們都動了它。這裡沒有鬼。"

msgid "There's a simple scientific explanation: it's called the ideomotor effect."
msgstr "這種現象有個簡單的科學解釋：名為意念動作效應。"

msgid "Simply put, just like your body reacts to pain reflexively, it may also react to ideas and move on its own. It pretty much bypasses the part of the brain which we use for conscious behavior."
msgstr "簡單來說，就像妳的身體會對疼痛做出反應，身體也會對想法反應並且自己行動。它繞過了我們大腦用來進行意識行為的部分。"

msgid "It's not all that different from blinking or breathing. The effect is even stronger when a bunch of gullible people who are desperate to believe in ghost stories get together and play."
msgstr "這跟眨眼或呼吸沒什麼差別。這種效應在一群容易受影響又非常相信鬼故事的人聚在一起玩遊戲時特別強烈。"

msgid "There was an experiment where the players were blindfolded and suddenly the \"ghosts\" could no longer spell messages. You can try it if you don't believe me."
msgstr "有個實驗讓玩家戴上眼罩後突然間\"鬼魂\"沒辦法再寫字了。不信的話妳們可以試試看。"

msgid "In other words, your mysterious answers from beyond... are really just your imagination playing tricks on you."
msgstr "換句話說，妳們來自另一個世界的訊息...只是妳們自己的想像在作祟。"

msgid "Great job killing the mood."
msgstr "謝謝妳潑冷水。"

msgid "You must be fun at parties."
msgstr "妳在派對上一定很受歡迎。"

msgid "Thanks a lot, Kat."
msgstr "還真是謝了，凱特。"

msgid "Always a pleasure."
msgstr "很高興能幫上忙。"

msgid "(Alright, time to search.)"
msgstr "(好，開始搜尋吧。)"

msgid "(I should go over my notes to make sure I don't forget anything.)"
msgstr "(我應該先讀過一次我的筆記以免忘了任何東西。)"

msgid "I already have enough chalk but... the more the merrier!"
msgstr "我的粉筆已經夠多了可是...越多越好！"

msgid "What kind of ritual is this...?"
msgstr "這到底是什麼儀式...？"

msgid "Do I really need all of this chalk...?"
msgstr "我真的需要這麼多粉筆嗎...？"

msgid "This window already has curtains."
msgstr "這扇窗戶已經有窗簾了。"

msgid "The thought of its burning beauty charms you."
msgstr "想到它燃燒的美貌讓你著迷。"

msgid "I really shouldn't, though."
msgstr "不過我真的不該這麼做。"

msgid "It looks like a private journal."
msgstr "看起來像是本個人日記。"

msgid "This looks like that girl's private journal."
msgstr "看起來像是那個女孩的個人日記。"

msgid "Look through it?"
msgstr "讀它嗎？"

msgid "Let's see..."
msgstr "讓我看看..."

msgid "Blegh, it's just math problems... and girly doodles all over."
msgstr "呃，只有數學問題...還有女孩子的塗鴉。"

msgid "This isn't worth my time."
msgstr "我沒時間看這些。"

msgid "A math notebook. Nothing worth looking through."
msgstr "一本數學筆記。沒什麼好看的。"

msgid "(Alright, so I need to search the school for the items first.)"
msgstr "(好，我應該先在學校找出我需要的物品。)"

msgid "(The rune should be in this room...)"
msgstr "(符石應該在這個房間裡...)"

msgid "(...somewhere.)"
msgstr "(...某個地方。)"

msgid "Well, I need a tuft of hair for the ritual..."
msgstr "好吧，我需要一束頭髮用來舉行儀式..."

msgid "Should I cut my own hair?"
msgstr "我應該剪下我自己的頭髮嗎？"

msgid "I guess..."
msgstr "應該吧..."

msgid "Forget it"
msgstr "算了"

msgid "Sigh..."
msgstr "唉..."

msgid "Here I go, I suppose..."
msgstr "來吧..."

msgid "I never want to do that again."
msgstr "我不想再做一次了。"

msgid "You're so brave, Kat."
msgstr "妳好勇敢，凱特。"

msgid "Of course not."
msgstr "當然不要。"

msgid "I already have enough hair."
msgstr "我已經有足夠的頭髮了。"

msgid "(Nah.)"
msgstr "(不要。)"

msgid "Um... any takers?"
msgstr "嗯...有人自願嗎？"

msgid "What do you need?"
msgstr "妳需要什麼？"

msgid "Just a bit of hair."
msgstr "一點頭髮就好。"

msgid "Why don't you cut your own?"
msgstr "為什麼妳不剪妳自己的？"

msgid "I thought you girls wanted to participate...?"
msgstr "我以為妳們想要有參與感...？"

msgid "I don't mind helping..."
msgstr "我不介意幫點忙..."

msgid "No Kaya, you don't have to do that."
msgstr "不，香耶，妳不需要這麼做。"

msgid "It's alright, I'll give you mine."
msgstr "沒關係，我可以給妳我的。"

msgid "...!"
msgstr "...！"

msgid "There's no need for that. I'll just cut some of mine."
msgstr "沒有必要那麼做。剪我的就好。"

msgid "Are you sure?"
msgstr "妳確定嗎？"

msgid "Yeah, it would be a waste to use yours."
msgstr "是啊，用妳的就太浪費了。"

msgid "Alright."
msgstr "好吧。"

msgid "A tuft of hair from Saki. She gave it to me voluntarily."
msgstr "一束沙紀的頭髮。她自願給我的。"

msgid "Thanks!"
msgstr "謝了！"

msgid "Uuugh..."
msgstr "呃~~..."

msgid "It's so dark..."
msgstr "好暗喔..."

msgid "Let's see what's behind this door."
msgstr "來看看門後有什麼。"

msgid "Maybe we'll find exam answers!"
msgstr "也許會有考卷答案！"

msgid "Or dead bodies!"
msgstr "或是屍體！"

msgid "Or... maybe it's just a supply closet."
msgstr "或是...只是置物間。"

msgid "Heh."
msgstr "呵。"
